name: Toedscool
flavorText: Toedscool lives in muggy forests. The flaps that fall from its body are chewy and very delicious.

previous.name: Brambleghast
previous.flavorText: It will open the branches of its head to envelop its prey. Once it absorbs all the life energy it needs, it expels the prey and discards it.

next.name: Toedscruel
next.flavorText: These Pokémon gather into groups and form colonies deep within forests. They absolutely hate it when strangers approach.
